OL,3,CMosques 'waiting months' for Home
OL,4,COffice security funding after attacks
OL,6,FAn organisation recording incidents of
OL,7,Fanti-Muslim hatred has complained of
OL,8,Fmosques "waiting for months" for
OL,9,Fsecurity funding promised by
OL,10,Fgovernment.
OL,12,FThe British Muslim Trust (BMT) said it
OL,13,Fhad noted 70 attacks at Muslim places
OL,14,Fof worship across the UK in the 12
OL,15,Fmonths to July, including vandalism
OL,16,Fand intimidation.
OL,26,@pD@IOUpD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
