OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784787487
OL,3,CMosques 'waiting months' for Home
OL,4,COffice security funding after attacks
OL,6,FThe data includes an arson attack at
OL,7,FPeacehaven Mosque in East Sussex in
OL,8,FOctober and an incident where bacon
OL,9,Fwas left at a mosque in Bristol during
OL,10,FFriday prayers in the first week of
OL,11,FRamadan in February.
OL,13,FOther incidents were cited as "online
OL,14,Fabuse", which the trust explained
OL,15,Foccurred in some cases where
OL,16,Fcommunities shared on social media
OL,17,Fthat an attack had taken place and
OL,18,Fwere met with death threats and
OL,19,Fencouragement of further trouble.
OL,26,@uD@_OUvD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784787487
OL,3,CMosques 'waiting months' for Home
OL,4,COffice security funding after attacks
OL,6,FBut BMT chief executive Akeela Ahmed
OL,7,Fsaid some mosques were waiting months
OL,8,Ffor funding after attacks because of a
OL,9,Fbacklog suggesting the #40 million pot
OL,10,Fcould be devolved from the Home Office
OL,11,Fto local areas potentially through
OL,12,Fmayoral authorities.
OL,14,FThe Government has said it is "working
OL,15,Fto process all applications as quickly
OL,16,Fas possible".
OL,26,@vD@_OUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784787487
OL,3,CMosques 'waiting months' for Home
OL,4,COffice security funding after attacks
OL,6,FOther incidents outside of the BMT
OL,7,Fstatistics include a replica of a
OL,8,Fmosque being placed on top of a
OL,9,Fbonfire in Northern Ireland, prompting
OL,10,Fwidespread condemnation, and a 14 year-
OL,11,Fold boy appearing in court earlier
OL,12,Fthis month charged with an offence
OL,13,Flinked to "extreme right-wing
OL,14,Fterrorism" after police discovered an
OL,15,Falleged plan to target two mosques in
OL,16,FSutton, south London.
OL,26,@uD@KOUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784787487
OL,3,CMosques 'waiting months' for Home
OL,4,COffice security funding after attacks
OL,6,FMs Ahmed said: "We are seeing a steady
OL,7,Frise in the number of attacks against
OL,8,Fmosques, and we believe the Government
OL,9,Fshould be doing everything it can to
OL,10,Fhelp mosques protect themselves.
OL,12,F"Asking for evidence that you're being
OL,13,Ftargeted is the equivalent of shutting
OL,14,Fthe stable door when the horse has
OL,15,Fbolted. A mosque is vulnerable purely
OL,16,Fbecause it's a mosque.
OL,26,@nD@POUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784787487
OL,3,CMosques 'waiting months' for Home
OL,4,COffice security funding after attacks
OL,6,F"Currently, they're waiting for
OL,7,Fmonths, while living in fear of
OL,8,Fanother attack, because of the
OL,9,Fbacklog. In many cases, police aren't
OL,10,Feven responding to low-level
OL,11,Fincidents, leaving people frightened
OL,12,Fand vulnerable.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784787487
OL,3,CMosques 'waiting months' for Home
OL,4,COffice security funding after attacks
OL,6,F"It is great that this funding and
OL,7,Finitiative exists, but we need to
OL,8,Frecognise that the momentum on attacks
OL,9,Fis building, and we need to react and
OL,10,Fprepare for this. Community members
OL,11,Fhave described, in their own words,
OL,12,Ffeeling 'scared for their life' and
OL,13,Ffeeling the need to 'protect
OL,14,Fthemselves' by staying at home in fear.
OL,16,F"We recommend exploring better ways to
OL,17,Fget the funding to mosques as smoothly
OL,18,Fas possible including that the fund is
OL,19,Fdevolved in order to speed up its
OL,20,Fdelivery, especially given recent
OL,21,Fevents."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
