OL,3,CMosques 'waiting months' for Home
OL,4,COffice security funding after attacks
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FA Home Office spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"Muslims in the UK face appalling
OL,13,Flevels of religious hate crime. It's
OL,14,Fcrucial that they not only are safe
OL,15,Fbut feel safe.
OL,17,F"This Government has increased funding
OL,18,Ffor protective security at mosques,
OL,19,FMuslim faith schools and community
OL,20,Fcentres to record levels ` up to #40
OL,21,Fmillion in 2026/27.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784787487
OL,3,CMosques 'waiting months' for Home
OL,4,COffice security funding after attacks
OL,6,F"We are working to process all
OL,7,Fapplications as quickly as possible."
OL,9,FThe latest annual Government data on
OL,10,Fpolice-recorded religious hate crime
OL,11,Fin England and Wales, published by the
OL,12,FHome Office in October, showed that
OL,13,Fanti-Muslim hate crime rose by almost
OL,14,Fa fifth from 2,690 offences recorded
OL,15,Fin the 12 months to March 2024 to
OL,16,F3,199 offences in the year ending
OL,17,FMarch 2025.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
