PN,38210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1784787487
OL,3,CMosques 'waiting months' for Home
OL,4,COffice security funding after attacks
OL,6,FThis week marks a year since the BMT
OL,7,Fwas appointed to receive investment
OL,8,Ffrom a Combatting Hate Against Muslims
OL,9,FFund.
OL,11,FThe trust brought together the Aziz
OL,12,FFoundation and Randeree Charitable
OL,13,FTrust and analyses data to help
OL,14,Fidentify the drivers behind a rise in
OL,15,Fanti-Muslim hatred.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/10
